However, looking at the January data only (which seems to be the focus since this is for an income statement), the only depreciation entry is on January 1, 2024, with the amount of 45746.47.

Since the problem is about calculating the depreciation item in the income statement and the January 1 entry is the only one within that month, I'll use that amount.
